# Multi-stage build: Build stage
FROM maven:3.11-eclipse-temurin-21 AS builder

WORKDIR /app

# Copy dependency files first (Rule 6: Cache dependency layers)
COPY pom.xml .
COPY src ./src

# Build JAR
RUN mvn clean package -DskipTests

# Multi-stage build: Runtime stage
FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine

WORKDIR /app

# Rule 10: EXPOSE documented
EXPOSE 3000

# Rule 11: LABEL metadata
LABEL maintainer="analytics-team@example.com"
LABEL version="1.0"
LABEL description="Java Analytics Dashboard - Metabase-like application"

# Rule 2: Non-root USER with UID 1001
RUN addgroup -g 1001 app && \
    adduser -u 1001 -D -h /app -s /bin/sh -G app app
USER app

# Rule 8: apt-get best practices with cache cleanup
# Install international fonts for PDF generation (fontconfig, ttf-dejavu)
RUN apk add --no-cache \
    fontconfig \
    ttf-dejavu \
    curl \
    && rm -rf /var/cache/apk/*

# Copy JAR from builder stage
COPY --from=builder /app/target/*.jar app.jar

# Rule 9: HEALTHCHECK present
# Health check against /api/health endpoint
HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:3000/api/health || exit 1

# Rule 12: CMD in exec form (JSON array)
# Rule 13: No ADD, only COPY
CMD ["java", "-jar", "/app/app.jar"]
